Director of Food & Beverage - Crowne Plaza Abu Dhabi Yas Island
01 May 2014 08:39 PM - UAE
. Crowne PlazaŽ hotels look for people who excel in their role, and arecommitted to delivering excellent experiences for guests. People who createconfidence, encourage success and make it happen! What's your passion? Whether you're into polka, painting or poloat InterContinental Hotel Group (IHG) we're interested in YOU! We employ peoplewho apply the same amount of care and passion to their jobs as they do theirhobbies - people who put our guests at the heart of everything they do. Andwe're looking for more people like this to join our friendly and professionalteam.   Set on the banks of the creek and along the Links ChampionshipGolf Course, Crowne Plaza hotel is located at on one of the country's mostambitious developments, Yas Island. The close proximity to the airport and only40 minutes into Abu Dhabi City makes this prime location an easy accessiblechoice for business & leisure travelers.   We are currently looking to recruit a Director of Food& Beverage who will be leading the Food & Beverage team andbrings the success of all Restaurant Outlets, Catering & Banquet to thenext level through delivering a winning guest experience.   The Director of Food & Beverage will establish and takesappropriate actions to achieve quality and guest satisfaction goals.   The Director of Food & Beverage has a thorough knowledge ofthe market as well as competition and ensures the compliance with allgovernmental regulations in terms of Food Safety.   In addition, the Director of Food & Beverage will beactively involved in the recruitment process of new F&B; team members andensures accurate job performance appraisal & coaching procedures are inplace for the entire team.   Further, the Director of Food & Beverage will be responsibleto prepare the annual departmental operating budget and monthly financial planswhilst continuously controlling productivity of all outlets. Identifyingadditional sales opportunities that enhances the maximum revenue is one of thetasks. The Director of Food & Beverage also monitors the departmental expenseswith a focus on Food & Beverage and labor cost.   The right candidate should have a solid F&B; background and aminimum of 2 years experience in a similar role in a 4 or 5 star hotel. Youneed to be innovative and highly revenue driven with a focus on guest andcolleagues satisfaction. Fluency in English with excellent administrative andorganizational skills are required. Knowledge of Micros and the UAEhotel/restaurant market is an advantage. As the Food & Beverage teamleader, the right candidate must be 'People Oriented' and have outstandingleadership and coaching skills.   In return we offer competitive pay and benefits, and a chance towork with a great team of talented people. Most importantly, we'll give you theRoom to be yourself. So what's your passion? Please get in touch if this position
